{"tid":2305260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★國泰貴賓室再裁百名員工　員工嘆搵工難感徬徨","createTime":"2020-11-29T13:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T16:42:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3d8d5a00b852d20787d8bb86d61bb34db001d2","tid":2305260,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:15:19.000Z","msg":"有傳營運商索迪斯獲政府保就業計劃補貼工資後仍要裁員。有索迪斯員工對本報投訴指，公司已收集員工資料、擬定名單，擬明日裁走約百名員工；民航工會表示亦有聽聞事件。索迪斯回覆時未有否認裁員一事，指明白員工的關注，會與員工保持緊密聯繫及溝通。<br />\n<br />\n國泰回覆指，有關機場貴賓室乃由第三方服務供應商索迪斯負責營運，就有關該公司與其員工的安排事宜，需直接聯絡該公司。而索迪斯則未有正面回應會否裁員，僅表示在疫情持續影響下，理解員工的關注，會與員工保持溝通。香港民用航空事業職工總會秘書長葉偉明指，有聽聞裁員事件，目前正在了解當中，並稱機場現時確實無生意，而保就業計劃亦將於本月底完結，預料未來會有更多公司裁員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201129/bkn-20201129010053695-1129_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201129%2Fbkn-20201129010053695-1129_00822_001.html&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=edf65a17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201129/bkn-20201129010053695-1129_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e85df841a1765e22e17801f41f7c73e3f42aac31","tid":2305260,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25cf3a5e2bd1ad71b03b5736518de2d85fa8e08","tid":2305260,"uid":56550,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T13:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><